      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">4.1007</ph> Solicitation alternative line item proposal.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d266e8" class="- topic/p ">Solicitations should be structured to allow offerors to propose alternative line items (see <xref href="4.1008.dita#FAR_4_1008"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">4.1008</xref> and <xref href="52.212-1.dita#FAR_52_212_1"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.212-1</xref>(e)). For example, when soliciting certain items using units of measure such as kit, set, or lot, the offeror may not be able to group and deliver all items in a single shipment.</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
